47:41.860 --> 47:45.113
The way you look right now.
Just the facts, ma'am.

47:47.824 --> 47:49.910
We slept over at the orphanage.

47:50.118 --> 47:52.746
Sometime... I didn't look at my watch,

47:52.829 --> 47:55.749
but the police report
said it was sometime after midnight,

47:55.832 --> 47:58.627
- we heard some...
